dct_description_sm: AMS 1 United States. Army Map Service [Great Britain. War Office. General Staff. Geographical Section.] G.S.G.S. no. 4380 United States. Army. Corps of Engineers Copied from an Italian map. Southern Italy grid convergence. Grid North is 0-degree 48' W of True North on this sheet. Relief is shown by hachures and contours.
